WorkSphere — Frontend Prototype

This single-file package includes index.html and app.js (added in the same document for convenience). It implements the requested features: sidebar with Unassigned Staff, Add New Worker modal with dynamic experiences and photo preview, floorplan with 6 zones, role-based assignment rules, per-zone capacity limits, remove (X) button, profile modal, responsive layout using Tailwind CSS, and simple animations.


---

